<font color="#ffffff">just do it by yourself.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

686
00:49:51,360 --> 00:49:52,760
<font color="#ffffff">Don't drag me into it.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

687
00:49:52,840 --> 00:49:56,840
<font color="#ffffff">I got information that Petch</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">is hiding out in a garden house<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

688
00:49:56,920 --> 00:49:58,040
<font color="#ffffff">around Bang Yai.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

689
00:49:58,120 --> 00:50:00,560
<font color="#ffffff">Really? You found him?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

690
00:50:00,640 --> 00:50:02,200
<font color="#ffffff">It's so quiet here.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

691
00:50:02,840 --> 00:50:04,120
<font color="#ffffff">Seems like nobody is here.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

692
00:50:04,200 --> 00:50:07,560
<font color="#ffffff">NEXT EPISODE</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

693
00:50:19,200 --> 00:50:24,080
<font color="#ffffff"><i>I wish I knew if I ever crossed your mind</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

694
