<font color="#ffffff"><i>I wish I knew if you heard the whisper</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

695
00:50:31,160 --> 00:50:37,120
<font color="#ffffff"><i>For my heart is crying out my love</i></font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff"><i>It's deep and true</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font></font>

696
00:50:37,200 --> 00:50:41,920
<font color="#ffffff"><i>But never reaching you</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

697
00:50:43,240 --> 00:50:48,040
<font color="#ffffff"><i>I know that it simply cannot be</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

698
00:50:49,240 --> 00:50:54,320
<font color="#ffffff"><i>And I never want to cause you misery</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

699
00:50:55,760 --> 00:51:00,920
<font color="#ffffff"><i>I'm just an ordinary man</i></font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff"><i>Worth nothing at all</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font></font>

700
00:51:01,720 --> 00:51:06,960
<font color="#ffffff"><i>And I never want to make</i></font><font color="#ffffff">
